WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:07.833
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for joining me today. I'm excited you're here. I have some things on my heart to talk about.

00:00:07.835 --> 00:00:17.701
I just wanted to point out what the Lord did whenever we had our prayer time yesterday. And you know, I never know what he's going to share.

00:00:17.702 --> 00:00:24.394
It's just amazing whenever you start praying and the Lord starts revealing things of the future to you.

00:00:24.395 --> 00:00:29.552
Less than 24 hours later, Trump announces his mineral deal.

00:00:29.553 --> 00:00:40.680
And I told you all I saw President Trump—if you watch the prayer time—if you are skipping out on the prayer time just to hear me talk a little bit and not praying with us, you are missing out.

00:00:40.681 --> 00:00:47.914
I encourage you to listen to the whole video, especially if you like to intercede and pray for the nations.

00:00:47.915 --> 00:00:58.213
I believe the Lord has called us to this YouTube channel; the primary focus is 'Prayer Changes Things.'And I believe we are changing things in nations.

00:00:58.214 --> 00:01:04.961
Yesterday, I feel like we went through the whole world. We were praying for elections and so many different things.

00:01:04.962 --> 00:01:11.678
The Lord had so many things on his heart that he wanted to talk about yesterday, obviously.

00:01:11.679 --> 00:01:19.528
But one of the major things was that I saw President Trump coming in. He looked like Uncle Sam.

00:01:19.529 --> 00:01:39.903
His hair was like it always is, but he had a patriotic outfit on—a red and white pinstripe suit and a stars and stripes jacket, like an American flag-looking jacket, and he had a top hat on.

00:01:39.904 --> 00:01:52.893
He flew in on a jet plane—it looked like an F-16—into Ukraine in this vision. Whenever he got there, he started negotiating.

00:01:52.894 --> 00:02:00.924
I kept hearing in the spirit realm, 'The Art of the Deal, the Art of the Deal.'He was making a deal yesterday with Zelensky and the Ukrainian people.

00:02:00.925 --> 00:02:01.024
I'm just going to go over a little bit of it because there are many of you who do not watch the prayer time.

00:02:01.025 --> 00:02:27.074
He was making a deal, and I saw him negotiating. I saw minerals. I could see mounds of dirt in the background in this vision.

00:02:27.075 --> 00:02:38.196
I could see conveyor belts with the dirt moving, and then I could see fish coming from the ocean; they were flayed in half and looked like a fishing industry.

00:02:38.197 --> 00:02:54.091
The Lord showed me the fishing industry and then bales of wheat that were all wrapped in bundles with a white-looking cloth.

00:02:54.093 --> 00:03:05.054
They were the whole stems—the wheat grain and all of the stalks.

00:03:05.055 --> 00:03:22.257
The back end of the wheat was pointing this way, and the ends of it that were cut were pointing in a bundle toward France. I could see it pointing toward France, laying down.

00:03:22.258 --> 00:03:38.691
The Lord was focusing my attention in the vision; I could see the round base of the stalks of the wheat wrapped in a bundle.

00:03:38.692 --> 00:03:54.130
He said, 'Brandon, this is in play as you speak right now. This is about to manifest.'I could hear it echoing inside of me that this major mineral deal was about to take place.

00:03:54.131 --> 00:04:16.159
Lo and behold, 24 hours later—after we uploaded that video that morning—they announced on the news that they had signed the mineral deal. So, we saw a prophetic word that was a 24-hour turnaround.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:31.813
That was a big deal to me because usually I wait months, or years sometimes, to see something, but I know there was an urgency to what we were praying over last night and interceding that this would get done—that this was a major domino.

00:04:31.814 --> 00:04:45.359
Then I saw Vladimir Putin with North Korea in the background with Xi Jinping and his allies.

00:04:45.360 --> 00:05:03.202
Vladimir Putin had a hand of red and white playing cards. He had five cards in his hand.

00:05:03.203 --> 00:05:20.736
They were big playing cards, and he was holding them out like a fan and hiding behind those cards, watching to see what was happening in Ukraine.

00:05:20.737 --> 00:05:34.459
I saw the words 'World War III'in black letters across. Then I remember the oil derrick—I think that was over the Mediterranean.

00:05:34.460 --> 00:05:37.818
Yes, because there were so many things the Lord showed us yesterday, folks.

00:05:37.819 --> 00:05:49.818
It was really interesting. Then the Lord showed me Germany, France, and then NATO. I saw an alliance.

00:05:49.819 --> 00:06:17.985
