00:06:17.986 --> 00:06:43.053
I saw a time span waiting behind those cards. But I heard the old USSR, the old Soviet Union, was with the KGB, and it was like roots inside Putin; he wants the whole thing, and he was looking for Kyiv.

00:06:43.054 --> 00:06:50.180
He wants the whole Ukraine. They were waiting for Trump to get out of the way.

00:06:50.181 --> 00:06:59.275
He has a plan, and in this plan, it was more evil. I could see the escalation of war.

00:06:59.276 --> 00:07:23.807
He was watching behind his playing cards, trying to play poker. A poker face.

00:07:23.808 --> 00:07:38.594
I saw North Korea siding with China as an Asian front in the days ahead, using Korea as a lynchpin.

00:07:38.595 --> 00:07:45.476
Eventually, I believe Kim Jong-un will be removed, and through his sister, there will be revival.

00:07:45.477 --> 00:07:58.157
I saw riots starting to take place in China—which we see in the news now—but I saw riots becoming more mainstream despite efforts to hush them down.

00:07:58.158 --> 00:08:16.079
Then it started to spread to other nations, like Canada, because of things that will be decided in the future that will be more suppressive, shutting up freedom of speech.

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:26.991
It will be more of a lockdown because of the way they think versus the way Christians think—great persecution coming to the Christians.

00:08:26.992 --> 00:08:36.848
Now, we got the emails. I don't mean to upset you all, but I have to speak what the Lord tells me to say regardless.

00:08:36.849 --> 00:08:49.599
It's not easy for me. I'm going to be real with you. It's very hard to come on here and tell you these words when I know it's going to upset people.

00:08:49.600 --> 00:08:58.057
Jeremiah had to do the same thing. I know your heart, and I know my job is not to scare you but to prepare you.

00:08:58.058 --> 00:09:10.174
I want to prepare you and sound the alarm as loud as I can for what the Spirit of the Lord is telling me to say, for I am accountable to him only, not to you.

00:09:10.175 --> 00:09:13.197
Now you say, 'Well, Brandon, I don't agree with you.'That's fine.

00:09:13.198 --> 00:09:22.079
Do you know how many millions of people—literally, I would say probably 10,000 a month at least—say something because they don't agree with me?

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:27.439
They are more vocal than a lot of you are with the nasty emails.

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:37.039
But you know what? I keep going because God said to. Persecution comes for the word's sake. You say I've missed it. That's fine. Keep watching.

00:09:37.040 --> 00:09:50.879
