00:09:50.880 --> 00:10:08.872
Folks, the prophets—I'm going to be just real bold with you right now—the prophetic people who spoke and told you that Joe Biden was going to be removed and that President Trump and all the prophetic words and everything that was spoken in 2020 were false prophecies.

00:10:08.873 --> 00:10:18.662
They missed it. But a lot of them didn't have the guts to come on and say, "We missed it."Instead, they kept kicking it down, going with QAnon and all the things they said.

00:10:18.663 --> 00:10:24.766
I'm not here to pick or poke at anybody; I'm here to tell you and shed light on things.

00:10:24.767 --> 00:10:34.434
If I miss it, I'm very quick to come on here and say, "Listen, I missed it."I don't have anything to hide from you. I don't answer to you; I answer to Him.

00:10:34.435 --> 00:10:47.935
And if I get in the flesh and I hear something off, then by my goodness, I want to say, "God, correct me, but make me stronger and make me sharper to hear You in these end times."I'm not ashamed.

00:10:47.936 --> 00:10:59.098
People pick at you all the time, but I'm telling you: I believe there are a lot of people telling you sugar-coated words about what is coming to Canada in the days ahead.

00:10:59.099 --> 00:11:07.147
